This paper deals with the design of a communication system with energy harvesting capabilities, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of several computer science subfields. However, the use of lattice codes and optimization techniques suggests that the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory). Other possible categories include cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.MM (Multimedia), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
